  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/14b10a7077e006fce8e9b09d4e293d9d.poster.avif?t=1741596212\" width=800 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/14b10a7077e006fce8e9b09d4e293d9d.webm?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/14b10a7077e006fce8e9b09d4e293d9d.mp4?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A classic gameplay with a modern roguelike twist!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the classic bubble matching gameplay with tons of new items and challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your mage, clear as many levels as possible, collect coins and reach the top of the tower!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Orbastical content!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >300+ hand crafted levels !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 items with special effects !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 different magic schools for unique challenges !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 cruel bosses !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovely pixel art and catchy chiptune audio</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/935414e7130250b200a76480456452aa.poster.avif?t=1741596212\" width=396 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/935414e7130250b200a76480456452aa.webm?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/935414e7130250b200a76480456452aa.mp4?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/54ce1af74c8123bbca0b9c4a2b244462.poster.avif?t=1741596212\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/54ce1af74c8123bbca0b9c4a2b244462.webm?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Addictive 1 button gameplay !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You only need to know how to hold a mouse and click to play ! </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/14b10a7077e006fce8e9b09d4e293d9d.poster.avif?t=1741596212\" width=800 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/14b10a7077e006fce8e9b09d4e293d9d.webm?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/14b10a7077e006fce8e9b09d4e293d9d.mp4?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A classic gameplay with a modern roguelike twist!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the classic bubble matching gameplay with tons of new items and challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your mage, clear as many levels as possible, collect coins and reach the top of the tower!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Orbastical content!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >300+ hand crafted levels !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 items with special effects !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 different magic schools for unique challenges !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 cruel bosses !</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovely pixel art and catchy chiptune audio</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/935414e7130250b200a76480456452aa.poster.avif?t=1741596212\" width=396 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/935414e7130250b200a76480456452aa.webm?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/935414e7130250b200a76480456452aa.mp4?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/54ce1af74c8123bbca0b9c4a2b244462.poster.avif?t=1741596212\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496500/extras/54ce1af74c8123bbca0b9c4a2b244462.webm?t=1741596212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Addictive 1 button gameplay !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You only need to know how to hold a mouse and click to play ! </p>",
